{"tid":2507754,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發！暫時有20多宗初步確診，均不屬於早前的群組個案","createTime":"2021-04-28T08:28:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T09:11:44.000Z","uid":5195,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e78f4015aa61e777b08a81c3fcf514db5919064a","tid":2507754,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T08:28:10.000Z","msg":"本港新增7宗新型冠狀病毒確診個案，1宗是本地關連個案，6宗是輸入病例，無源頭不明個案；<span class=\"red\">暫時有20多宗初步確診，均不屬於早前的群組個案</span>。 唯一一宗本地個案，患者是一名28歲家庭主婦，住在葵涌邨曉葵樓，是早前一名確診者的家居密切接觸者。她上星期六發病，由檢疫中心送院，衛生防護中心正追蹤她潛伏期內的行蹤。 至於6宗輸入個案，有2宗涉及菲律賓外傭，她們都驗出帶有N501Y變種病毒；1人是從印度入境本港的半歲女嬰；其餘3宗則來自尼泊爾。6人分別在何文田九龍維景酒店、旺角帝盛酒店，以及荃灣遠東絲麗酒店檢疫 。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2389215\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2389215&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0lDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=60ed0f2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2389215</a>"},{"pid":"281802bd469c6486f5e9724a10fe89fc4061e7ef","tid":2507754,"uid":82938,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T08:28:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />輸入個案味唔屬於"},{"pid":"27ca38171eda31fc6c3f79c7b935c67cf52fb996","tid":2507754,"uid":191300,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T08:29:23.000Z","msg":"印度，菲律賓，尼泊爾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"304001f4b667aa13bf468832e161c114848ba402","tid":2507754,"uid":4243,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T08:31:58.000Z","msg":"出黎話搖錯樽咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59e0727c397e740865930f6dfd39303bf73e08ae","tid":2507754,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T08:36:54.000Z","msg":"聽住先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba5f6